00:02:21.680 --> 00:02:24.020
the acting deputy director
of the Library of Congress

00:02:24.020 --> 00:02:26.430
who will introduce
our keynote speaker,

00:02:26.430 --> 00:02:27.900
Representative Mark Takano.

00:02:27.900 --> 00:02:29.700
Thank you.

00:02:29.700 --> 00:02:36.530
